OL,3,CEurovision winner Dara arrives home to
OL,4,Cscreaming fans in Bulgaria
OL,6,FHundreds of cheering fans carrying
OL,7,Fhomemade signs and waving Bulgarian
OL,8,Fflags welcomed Eurovision Song Contest
OL,9,Fwinner Dara upon her return home on
OL,10,FSunday.
OL,12,FVisibly tired but smiling, the 27-year-
OL,13,Fold singer arrived at Sofia's Vasil
OL,14,FLevski Airport waving the Eurovision
OL,15,Ftrophy.
OL,17,F"This award marks the beginning of my
OL,18,Ffuture international career," Dara
OL,19,Fsaid as she arrived.
