OL,3,CEurovision winner Dara arrives home to
OL,4,Cscreaming fans in Bulgaria
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe singer was the surprise winner of
OL,12,Fthe 70th Eurovision Song Contest in
OL,13,FVienna on Saturday, with her catchy
OL,14,Fparty anthem "Bangaranga" giving
OL,15,FBulgaria its first-ever victory in the
OL,16,Fcompetition.
OL,26,@vD@NOUvD@YO]
