OL,3,CEurovision winner Dara arrives home to
OL,4,Cscreaming fans in Bulgaria
OL,6,F"We have done something great for
OL,7,FBulgarian music, and I hope this sends
OL,8,Fa message that Bulgaria's performers
OL,9,Fand artists deserve stronger support,"
OL,10,FDara said.
OL,12,FThe performer described Bulgaria as
OL,13,F"an exceptionally talented nation that
OL,14,Fwill continue to receive more and more
OL,15,Fattention".
