OL,3,CEurovision winner Dara arrives home to
OL,4,Cscreaming fans in Bulgaria
OL,6,FDara, whose real name is Darina
OL,7,FYotova, beat 24 other competitors
OL,8,Fduring Saturday's grand final of the
OL,9,FEuropean pop music competition,
OL,10,Fagainst a backdrop of boycotts and
OL,11,Fprotest.
OL,13,FIreland, Iceland, the Netherlands,
OL,14,FSpain and Slovenia all quit the
OL,15,Fcompetition over Israel's inclusion,
OL,16,Fand demonstrators marched outside the
OL,17,Farena ahead of the live final.
OL,19,FIn the end, Israel came in second,
OL,20,Fwith Noam Bettan scoring 343 points
OL,21,Ffor his song Michelle.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
