OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779066195
OL,3,CEurovision winner Dara arrives home to
OL,4,Cscreaming fans in Bulgaria
OL,6,FDara won 516 points for her tightly
OL,7,Fchoreographed performance, which
OL,8,Fproved a hit with both national juries
OL,9,Fin participating countries and viewers
OL,10,Faround the world, whose votes together
OL,11,Fdecide the winner.
OL,13,F"I want to thank my husband, because
OL,14,Fhe was the one to push me to come to
OL,15,FEurovision," Dara said immediately
OL,16,Fafter her win.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
