PN,30906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779066195
OL,3,CEurovision winner Dara arrives home to
OL,4,Cscreaming fans in Bulgaria
OL,6,F"Because in the beginning I was not
OL,7,Fsure if I want to come or not, because
OL,8,FI had anxiety and doubt with myself,
OL,9,Fand he was the one that he just pushed
OL,10,Fme, and he was like, 'you need to go
OL,11,Fright now to Eurovision, right now,
OL,12,Fpick up your phone tell them you're
OL,13,Fgoing'."
OL,15,FSofia Mayor Vassil Terziev was among
OL,16,Fthe officials to welcome Dara at the
OL,17,Fairport and said the capital city is
OL,18,Fready to host the 2027 contest - the
OL,19,Fsame year Bulgaria will mark its 20th
OL,20,Fanniversary of joining the European
OL,21,FUnion.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
