OL,3,CEurovision winner Dara arrives home to
OL,4,Cscreaming fans in Bulgaria
OL,6,FThe Balkan country's political leaders
OL,7,Falso joined the show of national
OL,8,Fpride, with President Iliana Yotova
OL,9,Fcalling the win a "triumph for
OL,10,FBulgaria" and Prime Minister Rumen
OL,11,FRadev proclaiming it "a victory with
OL,12,Fglobal resonance".
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
